stk = zeros(50);
stp = zeros(50);
for i in 1:50
    a = wtedChimera(10000,i);
    ak = akpw(a);
    stk[i] = sum(compStretches(ak,a))/nnz(a);
    ap = randishPrim(a);
    stp[i] = sum(compStretches(ap,a))/nnz(a);
end
